## How to Run

### Python Programs
```bash
# Navigate to the Python directory
python even_odd.py
python largest_number.py
python grade_calculator.py
python login_validation.py
python password_checker.py
```

### C Programs
```bash
# Compile
gcc even_odd.c -o even_odd
gcc largest_number.c -o largest_number
gcc grade_calculator.c -o grade_calculator
gcc login_validation.c -o login_validation
gcc password_checker.c -o password_checker

# Run
./even_odd
./largest_number
./grade_calculator
./login_validation
./password_checker
```

